   Official download sites    Official download sites  

There are three ways to get the newest version of Tag-o-Miga and TMTags.  
    	
    The official Web page, run by myself.  Go to URL @{" " link "HTTP://SURF.TO/RICHARDS.PAGE/MAIN"} http://surf.to/richards.page and follow the Tag-o-Miga link.  If surf.to is not available, try http://www.frontier.u-net.com instead.  Alpha and beta versions of Tag-o-Miga are ONLY available from this location. 
    	
    Digital Dilemma BBS.  FREQ TAGOMIGA from 2:255/90 for information on the available downloads.  The telephone number is +44(0)1626-821110 and the BBS is open 24 hours a day. 
    	
    Aminet.  The filename is comm/misc/TagoMiga.lha (Amiga version only) or comm/misc/TagoMigaSrc.lha.   
